snippet.title: Yoshi's Island: SMW2+ Hack 1-1 100% in 1:14 - Theory TAS
snippet.description:
Watch live at twitch.tv/brooklyn9d5

1385 re-records. Mostly played at 50% speed and faster, on a real SNES controller. No frame advance.

SMW2+ is the first complete mod of SMW2: Yoshi's Island ever. Made by Golden Yoshi in 2005. Download here: http://goo.gl/hRHNXQ

100% means collecting 30 stars, 20 red coins and 5 flowers. I used RTA timing. (begins on the frame "10" appears. Timing stops on the frame Yoshi begins to throw Baby Mario)
